name: Love, Death <3
description: made by Alfred Swahn. Quantity: 5. (To me death is this beatiful and pretty simple phenomenom that I can't seem to get away from. I love how skulls look in drawing and art pieces, and how some people feel discomfort while others just think it's fucking sick! I adore the fact that once we all die in the end we only leave our skeleton behind. No matter your race, gender or history, in the end we're all equal.)
